\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw15 \cltxlrtb\clftsWidth3\clwWidth1188 \cellx1080\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw15 
\cltxlrtb\clftsWidth3\clwWidth3420 \cellx4500\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrl\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrb\brdrs\brdrw15 \clbrdrr\brdrs\brdrw15 \cltxlrtb\clftsWidth3\clwWidth3914 \cellx8414\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\intbl\faauto\rin0\lin0 {
\f0\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 1. \cell A method based existence check is executed which uses an XPath Boolean condition. It evaluates to true and uses the default value for }{\f0\highlight8 onConditionTrue}{\f0 .}{\f0\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 
\cell Pass\cell }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {\f0\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 \trowd \trgaph108\trleft-108\trftsWidth1\trpaddl108\trpaddr108\trpaddfl3\trpaddfr3 \clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\brdrw15 
